::: {.cell-output-display}
![찹쌀 급식시장 요인별 분석 그래프](proj_school_files/figure-html/fig-school-meal-unit-price-analysis-1.png){#fig-school-meal-unit-price-analysis fig-align='center' width=90%}
:::
:::








